1. 下载
url: https://download.docker.com/win/stable/DockerToolbox.exe

2.加入共享文件夹
打开Vbox设置
/d/Docker /d/Docker

3.加速docker hub
$ docker-machine ssh default	//连接到虚拟机
$ sudo vi /var/lib/boot2docker/profile
<---------------
EXTRA_ARGS='--registry-mirror=https://registry.docker-cn.com
---------------->
$ exit
$ docker-machine restart default

4.git-bash运行docker
$ cd /d/Program\ Files/Docker\ Toolbox/
$ ./start.sh
